lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur's Kyle Walker says Nathaniel Clyne will receive his full support if the Liverpool right back is picked ahead of him for England's opening Euro 2016 Group B match against Russia in Marseille on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Walker Will Support Rival Clyne if He Wins England Spot
headline.main: Walker Will Support Rival Clyne if He Wins England Spot
